# =====================================================================
#  STREAMLIT CLOUD SECRETS TEMPLATE
# =====================================================================
#  This file is a TEMPLATE. Do NOT commit a real secrets.toml with your
#  actual key — it's already listed in .gitignore.
#
#  How to use on Streamlit Cloud:
#    1. Go to your app on https://share.streamlit.io
#    2. Click the three dots menu → "Settings" → "Secrets"
#    3. Paste the contents below and fill in your real values
#    4. Click "Save". The app will restart automatically.
#
#  How to use locally:
#    Either copy this file to .streamlit/secrets.toml with real values,
#    OR use the .env file (see .env.example) — both work.
#
#  NOTE: Azure endpoint, deployment names, and API version are now
#  hard-coded in assessment_logic/llm_client.py (CAPSTONE_CONFIG).
#  You only need to set the API key here.
# =====================================================================

